item.title: How do i make a place wild?
item.dc:creator: @CoonHunter CoonHunter
item.description:
@CoonHunter wrote:

The problem is not that you need to make it wild, its that you need to make it not safe again, i know that is confusing but eeh, idfc. There should be cords in there reguarding the safe spots. Just find the top left corner of it, and then find it in this boolean.

public boolean nonwild
